  "comment": "SB02 SHOWBAR on Battery with Derby and PAR effects: The SB02 ShowBar kit is a rechargeable lithium battery powered Show Bar containing 4 effects mounted on a DMX T-bar. It ‘s equipped with 2 LED Derby effect lights and a pair of high power LED pars that guarantee a stunning light show. The T-bar can be controlled in auto mode, sound activated mode or 6/30-channel DMX mode and is also equipped with an IR sensor for controlling on distance by remote control. The SB02 ShowBar can be mounted on the included stand and the capacity of the battery can easily be read on the battery indicator.\n\n\n",
